                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>When an alchemical golem takes physical damage from a critical hit or is affected by a <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Shatter]{Shatter}</em> spell, one glass chamber within its body shatters, spewing alchemical liquid in a <span data-pf2-effect-area=\"emanation\" data-pf2-distance=\"5\">5-foot emanation</span>.</p>\n<p>Roll on the alchemical chambers list (see above) to determine which one shatters-on a roll of 1-5, creatures in the area take [[/r {10d6}[damage]]]{10d6 damage} of the appropriate type (<span data-pf2-check=\"reflex\" data-pf2-dc=\"28\" data-pf2-traits=\"damaging-effect\" data-pf2-label=\"Alchemical Rupture DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Reflex</span>). On a roll of 6, creatures must instead save against the sickness effect.</p>\n<hr />\n<table class=\"pf2-table\" style=\"width: 98.9637%; height: 251px;\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height: 29px;\">\n<th style=\"width: 9.5986%; height: 29px;\"><a class=\"inline-roll roll\" title=\"Alchemical Effect\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"Alchemical Effect\" data-formula=\"d6\"> d6</a></th>\n<th style=\"width: 90.2269%; height: 29px;\">Alchemical Effect</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 29px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 9.5986%; height: 29px;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 90.2269%; height: 29px;\">\n<p>[[/r {10d6}[acid]]]{10d6 acid damage} <span data-pf2-check=\"reflex\" data-pf2-dc=\"28\" data-pf2-traits=\"acid,damaging-effect\" data-pf2-label=\"Alchemical Rupture DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Reflex</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 29px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 9.5986%; height: 29px;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"width: 90.2269%; height: 29px;\">[[/r {10d6}[cold]]]{10d6 cold damage} <span data-pf2-check=\"reflex\" data-pf2-dc=\"28\" data-pf2-traits=\"cold, damaging-effect\" data-pf2-label=\"Alchemical Rupture DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Reflex</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 29px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 9.5986%; height: 29px;\">3</td>\n<td style=\"width: 90.2269%; height: 29px;\">[[/r {10d6}[electricity]]]{10d6 electricity damage} <span data-pf2-check=\"reflex\" data-pf2-dc=\"28\" data-pf2-traits=\"electricity,damaging-effect\" data-pf2-label=\"Alchemical Rupture DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Reflex</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 29px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 9.5986%; height: 29px;\">4</td>\n<td style=\"width: 90.2269%; height: 29px;\">[[/r {10d6}[fire]]]{10d6 fire damage} <span data-pf2-check=\"reflex\" data-pf2-dc=\"28\" data-pf2-traits=\"fire,damaging-effect\" data-pf2-label=\"Alchemical Rupture DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Reflex</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 29px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 9.5986%; height: 29px;\">5</td>\n<td style=\"width: 90.2269%; height: 29px;\">[[/r {10d6}[poison]]]{10d6 poison damage} <span data-pf2-check=\"reflex\" data-pf2-dc=\"28\" data-pf2-traits=\"poison,damaging-effect\" data-pf2-label=\"Alchemical Rupture DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Reflex</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 77px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 9.5986%; height: 77px;\">6</td>\n<td style=\"width: 90.2269%; height: 77px;\">Sickness: <span data-pf2-check=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-traits=\"disease\" data-pf2-label=\"Alchemical Sickness DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"26\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Fortitude</span> Save or @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 1} (@Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 2} on a critical failure)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>"
